javanews.events.table
Class RowListener

java.lang.Object
  javanews.events.table.RowListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener
public class RowListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener

This class is to be attached to instances of JTable shown within the main GUI windows. It is responsible for listening for user-generated mouse clicks either on entries in the messages table or the list of links. Once received the class determines which table generated the event and calls the appropriate methods.

1.000
